OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a dry morning, with
OL,7,Fprolonged spells of sunshine. A hot
OL,8,Fafternoon to come, with light winds
OL,9,Facross the country and plenty of hazy
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine to end the
OL,13,Fday. Dry overnight, with some low
OL,14,Fcloud returning to eastern areas,
OL,15,Fwestern areas holding on to the
OL,16,Fclearer skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
