OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Remaining hot, though a
OL,9,Flittle cooler towards the northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fdry into the weekend, with sunny
OL,13,Fspells by day and clear skies at
OL,14,Fnight. Temperatures trending a little
OL,15,Fnearer to average, but still feeling
OL,16,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
